                     <interp inst="t18250407-149-person833" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am an officer. I took the prisoner, as Mark's charged him with the robbery; I took off his hat, and found the cap and white trowsers in it; he had corderoy trowsers on.</p>
